# Chrome Extension App Structure (2025) — MV3 + Side Panel

**Goal:** Standardize structure for background (service worker), content scripts, side panel UI, popup & options UIs, shared modules, and automation flows. Ensures reliable state across navigations and clean build outputs.

> Build context: app uses Vite multi-build and copies MV3 artifacts into `dist/` during `nx build`.

## Directory Layout

```text
apps/automation-chrome-ext/
├─ src/
│  ├─ manifest.json
│  ├─ background/               # MV3 service worker (durable orchestration & messaging)
│  │  ├─ index.ts
│  │  ├─ lifecycle.ts           # service worker lifecycle management
│  │  ├─ messaging.ts           # typed messaging contracts
│  │  └─ storage.ts             # durable state storage with chrome.storage
│  ├─ content/                  # Content scripts (page automation + site adapters)
│  │  ├─ index.ts
│  │  ├─ dom/
│  │  │  ├─ wait.ts             # robust waitFor*, auto-retry, visibility guards
│  │  │  ├─ query.ts            # functional DOM querying utilities
│  │  │  └─ actions.ts          # reliable element interactions with retries
│  │  ├─ sites/
│  │  │  ├─ freshsales/
│  │  │  │  ├─ search.ts        # search field interactions
│  │  │  │  ├─ openContact.ts   # navigate to first result URL
│  │  │  │  └─ marketing.ts     # show-all + field edits (digital/ooh)
│  │  │  └─ callrail/
│  │  │     ├─ activity.ts
│  │  │     └─ pagination.ts
│  ├─ sidepanel/                # Side panel UI (per-tab tools / status)
│  │  ├─ index.html
│  │  ├─ index.tsx
│  │  └─ ui/                    # reusable UI components
│  │     ├─ Button.tsx
│  │     ├─ StatusIndicator.tsx
│  │     └─ LogViewer.tsx
│  ├─ popup/                    # Browser action popup
│  │  ├─ index.html
│  │  └─ index.ts
│  ├─ options/
│  │  ├─ index.html
│  │  └─ index.ts
│  ├─ automation/               # High-level flows & step runner
│  │  ├─ flows/
│  │  │  ├─ freshsales/
│  │  │  │  ├─ searchAndOpenContact.ts
│  │  │  │  └─ updateMarketingFields.ts
│  │  │  └─ callrail/
│  │  │     └─ downloadActivityCsv.ts
│  │  ├─ steps.ts               # typed step config + dispatcher
│  │  └─ orchestrator.ts        # tab-scoped orchestration; resumes across navigations
│  ├─ common/                   # Shared modules (no DOM)
│  │  ├─ types/
│  │  │  └─ index.ts            # TypeScript type definitions
│  │  ├─ constants.ts           # app-wide constants and configuration
│  │  ├─ logging.ts             # centralized logging with levels and context
│  │  ├─ messaging.ts           # typed messages; port/connect helpers
│  │  ├─ state.ts               # durable state management and persistence
│  │  └─ utils.ts               # common utility functions
│  └─ tests/
│     ├─ unit/                  # vitest/jest unit tests
│     └─ e2e/                   # Playwright E2E specs, fixtures, config
│        ├─ playwright.config.ts
│        ├─ fixtures/
│        └─ specs/
├─ docs/
│  ├─ README.md                 # documentation guide
│  ├─ html-snapshots/           # HTML snapshots for debugging and testing
│  └─ flows/                    # human-readable flow documentation
│     └─ freshsales-contact-lookup.md
├─ tools/
│  └─ debug/
│     ├─ debug-connection.ts    # connection debugging utilities
│     └─ debug-pagination.ts    # pagination analysis and testing tools
├─ data/
│  └─ fixtures/                 # test data fixtures
│     ├─ sample-contacts.json
│     └─ sample-flows.json
├─ vite.config.ts
├─ vite.config.content.ts
├─ tsconfig.json
├─ project.json                 # nx targets (build / e2e)
├─ package.json
└─ README.md